### Video Games Sales Dataset


This dataset comprises a list of video games with sales exceeding 100,000 copies, sourced from vgchartz.com. It includes various attributes for each game to analyze trends and patterns in the video game industry.

#### Matrix Column Entries (Attributes):

- **Rank**: Overall sales ranking of the game.
- **Name**: Name of the game.
- **Platform**: Platform on which the game was released (e.g., PC, PS4).
- **Year**: Year when the game was released.
- **Genre**: Genre of the game.
- **Publisher**: Publisher of the game.
- **NA_Sales**: Sales in North America (in millions).
- **EU_Sales**: Sales in Europe (in millions).
- **JP_Sales**: Sales in Japan (in millions).
- **Other_Sales**: Sales in the rest of the world (in millions).
- **Global_Sales**: Total worldwide sales (in millions).

#### Libraries Used

```python
import os               # Paths to files
import numpy as np      # Linear algebra
import pandas as pd     # Data processing
